main event: A UFO was sighted in Labrador on November 6, 1954, moving slowly across the sky.
interesting points: The object was elliptical in shape and approximately 25-30 feet in diameter,The object emitted two small explosions and then disappeared in a large explosion of blue light,The sighting lasted approximately 2-3 minutes and occurred at around 4:30 PM,No trails, vapors, or sounds were observed during the sighting,The conclusion was categorized as astronomical, suggesting it was a meteor.
sighted object: an elliptical white or silver object
